# Kapalishwar — Astro Starter

A tiny Tamil-style "temple of text" starter.

## Develop
```bash
npm install
npm run dev

npm run build

---

## Pages (inside `src/pages/`)

You’ll need to create a folder called `src/pages` in your repo, then add these files:

---

### 6. `src/pages/index.astro`
```astro
---
const tiers = [1,2,3,4,5,6,7];
---
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Kapalishwar — Temple of Text</title>
    <style>
      body{font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;line-height:1.6;margin:0}
      header,main{max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:2rem}
      nav a{margin-right:1rem}
      .tiers a{display:inline-block;margin:0.25rem 0.5rem}
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <h1>kapalishwar.com</h1>
      <p>A small Tamil-style temple of text. Gateway → Sanctum → Halls → Tiers.</p>
      <nav>
        <a href="/sanctum">Sanctum</a>
        <a href="/reflections">Reflections</a>
        <a href="/glossary">Glossary</a>
      </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
      <h2>Gopura Tiers</h2>
      <p class="tiers">
        {tiers.map(n => (<a href={`/tier/${n}/`}>Tier {n}</a>))}
      </p>
      <p>This is a starter. Replace copy with your own writing.</p>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Sanctum — Kapalishwar</title>
    <style>
      body{font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;line-height:1.6;max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:2rem}
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Sanctum</h1>
    <p>Place 3–5 core Codex essays here. This page is your <em>garbha gṛha</em>.</p>
  </body>
</html>

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Reflections — Kapalishwar</title>
    <style>
      body{font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;line-height:1.6;max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:2rem}
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Reflections</h1>
    <p>Short notes, bilingual fragments, dream entries — your <em>ardha-mandapa</em>.</p>
  </body>
</html>

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Glossary — Kapalishwar</title>
    <style>
      body{font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;line-height:1.6;max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:2rem}
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
